---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = "朝圣故事 | Kailash 2026";
const description = "来自世界各地朝圣者的真实故事。冈仁波齐转山之旅如何改变他们的人生，带来心灵的觉醒与转变。";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <div class="pt-20">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="bg-kailash-dark py-16">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4" data-lang-content="zh">朝圣故事</h1>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Pilgrim Stories</h1>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">巡礼者の物語</h1>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">순례자 이야기</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/80" data-lang-content="zh">真实旅程 · 心灵转变 · 神圣回忆</p>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/80" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Real Journeys · Transformative Experiences · Sacred Memories</p>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/80" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">真実の旅 · 心の変容 · 神聖な思い出</p>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/80" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">진실한 여정 · 마음의 변화 · 신성한 추억</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Featured Story with Photo -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-kailash-light">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="relative aspect-[4/3] md:aspect-auto bg-gray-100">
              <img src="/images/story-featured.jpg" alt="朝圣者在卓玛拉垭口" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" loading="eager" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.parentElement.querySelector('.fallback').style.display='flex';" />
              <div class="fallback absolute inset-0 bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400" style="display: none;">
                <span>图片加载失败</span>
              </div>
              <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/70 to-transparent p-4">
                <p class="text-white font-semibold" data-lang-content="zh">卓玛拉垭口 · 5648米</p>
                <p class="text-white font-semibold" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Drolma La Pass · 5648m</p>
                <p class="text-white font-semibold" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">ドマラ峠 · 5648m</p>
                <p class="text-white font-semibold" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">도마라 고개 · 5648m</p>
                <p class="text-white/80 text-sm">2024年9月 · 张先生</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8 flex flex-col justify-center">
              <div class="text-kailash-gold mb-4">★★★★★</div>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic text-lg leading-relaxed" data-lang-content="zh">"当翻越卓玛拉垭口的那一刻，我终于明白什么是信仰的力量。5630米，这是我人生到达的最高点，也是心灵的最高点。"</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic text-lg leading-relaxed" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">"The moment I crossed Drolma La pass, I finally understood the power of faith. At 5,630 meters, this is the highest point of my life, and also the highest point of my soul."</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic text-lg leading-relaxed" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">"ドマラ峠を越えた瞬間、信仰の力とは何かを初めて理解しました。標高5630メートル、これは私の人生で最も高い地点であり、同時に心の最も高い地点でもあります。"</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 italic text-lg leading-relaxed" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">"도마라 고개를 넘는 순간, 신앙의 힘이 무엇인지 처음으로 이해했습니다. 해발 5630미터, 이것은 제 인생에서 가장 높은 곳이자 동시에 마음의 가장 높은 곳입니다."</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-kailash-gold/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">张</div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-medium text-lg" data-lang-content="zh">张先生</p>
                  <p class="font-medium text-lg" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Mr. Zhang</p>
                  <p class="font-medium text-lg" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">張さん</p>
                  <p class="font-medium text-lg" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">장 씨</p>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">北京 · 2025年9月</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Stories Grid with Photos -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-4" data-lang-content="zh">更多朝圣故事</h2>
          <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-4" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">More Pilgrim Stories</h2>
          <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-4" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">その他の巡礼者の物語</h2>
          <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-4" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">더 많은 순례자 이야기</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Story 1 -->
          <div class="bg-kailash-light rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-md">
            <div class="relative aspect-[4/3] bg-gray-100">
              <img src="/images/story-1.jpg" alt="李女士与母亲在止热寺" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.parentElement.querySelector('.fallback').style.display='flex';" />
              <div class="fallback absolute inset-0 bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400" style="display: none;">
                <span>图片加载失败</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <div class="text-kailash-gold mb-3">★★★★★</div>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic text-sm" data-lang-content="zh">"带着70岁的母亲完成转山，她在止热寺前双手合十的样子，是我这辈子见过最美的画面。"</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic text-sm" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">"I completed the kora with my 70-year-old mother. Watching her pray at Drirapuk Monastery was the most beautiful sight I've ever seen."</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic text-sm" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">"70歳の母と共にコーラを完成させました。ディラプク寺で母が手を合わせる姿は、私が今まで見た中で最も美しい光景でした。"</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic text-sm" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">"70세 어머니와 함께 코라를 완주했습니다. 디라푹 사원에서 어머니가 손을 모으는 모습은 제가 지금까지 본 것 중 가장 아름다운 광경이었습니다."</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-kailash-gold/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">李</div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-medium text-sm" data-lang-content="zh">李女士</p>
                  <p class="font-medium text-sm" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Ms. Li</p>
                  <p class="font-medium text-sm" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">李さん</p>
                  <p class="font-medium text-sm" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">이 씨</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">成都 · 2025年6月</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Story 2 -->
          <div class="bg-kailash-light rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-md">
            <div class="relative aspect-[4/3] bg-gray-100">
              <img src="/images/story-2.jpg" alt="Rajesh Kumar在冈仁波齐" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.parentElement.querySelector('.fallback').style.display='flex';" />
              <div class="fallback absolute inset-0 bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400" style="display: none;">
                <span>图片加载失败</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <div class="text-kailash-gold mb-3">★★★★★</div>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic text-sm">"Kailash is the abode of Lord Shiva. I waited 3 years for the permit. The 52km kora changed my perspective on life forever."</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-kailash-gold/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">R</div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-medium text-sm">Rajesh Kumar</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Delhi, India · 2024</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Story 3 -->
          <div class="bg-kailash-light rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-md">
            <div class="relative aspect-[4/3] bg-gray-100">
              <img src="/images/story-3.jpg" alt="Sarah Johnson在转山途中" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.parentElement.querySelector('.fallback').style.display='flex';" />
              <div class="fallback absolute inset-0 bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400" style="display: none;">
                <span>图片加载失败</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <div class="text-kailash-gold mb-3">★★★★★</div>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic text-sm" data-lang-content="zh">"作为一名基督徒，我不确定会发生什么。但冈仁波齐超越了任何单一宗教。站在那座神圣的山峰前，我感受到了无法言喻的存在。"</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic text-sm" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">"As a Christian, I wasn't sure what to expect. But Kailash transcends any single religion. Standing before that sacred peak, I felt a presence that words cannot describe."</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic text-sm" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">"クリスチャンとして、何が待っているか分かりませんでした。しかしカイラスはあらゆる宗教を超越しています。あの神聖な峰の前に立つと、言葉では表現できない存在感を感じました。"</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic text-sm" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">"기독교인으로서 무엇이 기다리고 있을지 확신하지 못했습니다. 하지만 카일라스는 어떤 단일 종교도 뛰어넘습니다. 그 신성한 봉우리 앞에 서자, 말로 표현할 수 없는 존재감을 느꼈습니다."</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-kailash-gold/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">S</div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-medium text-sm">Sarah Johnson</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">London, UK · 2024</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Story 4 -->
          <div class="bg-kailash-light rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-md">
            <div class="relative aspect-[4/3] bg-gray-100">
              <img src="/images/story-4.jpg" alt="Tenzin Dorje第七次转山" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.parentElement.querySelector('.fallback').style.display='flex';" />
              <div class="fallback absolute inset-0 bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400" style="display: none;">
                <span>图片加载失败</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <div class="text-kailash-gold mb-3">★★★★★</div>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic text-sm" data-lang-content="zh">"这是我的第七次转山。每次我都能发现新的东西。山没有变，但我变了。每一圈都剥离了另一层自我，揭示出更真实的本我。"</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic text-sm" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">"This was my seventh kora. Each time I discover something new. The mountain doesn't change, but I do. Every circuit peels away another layer of ego, revealing a more authentic self."</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic text-sm" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">"これは7回目のコーラでした。毎回新しい発見があります。山は変わらないが、私は変わる。一周ごとに自我の層が剥がれ、より真実の自分が現れる。"</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic text-sm" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">"이것은 제 7번째 코라였습니다. 매번 새로운 것을 발견합니다. 산은 변하지 않지만, 저는 변합니다. 매 바퀴가 자아의 또 다른 층을 벗겨내어 더 진실한 자신을 드러냅니다."</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-kailash-gold/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">丁</div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-medium text-sm">Tenzin Dorje</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Lhasa, Tibet · 2024</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Story 5 -->
          <div class="bg-kailash-light rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-md">
            <div class="relative aspect-[4/3] bg-gray-100">
              <img src="/images/story-5.jpg" alt="韩国朝圣团" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.parentElement.querySelector('.fallback').style.display='flex';" />
              <div class="fallback absolute inset-0 bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400" style="display: none;">
                <span>图片加载失败</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <div class="text-kailash-gold mb-3">★★★★★</div>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic text-sm" data-lang-content="zh">"我为了冒险而来，却带着转变的心离开。韩国朝圣团成为了我的家人。我们一起受苦，一起欢笑，一起成长。"</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic text-sm" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">"I came for the adventure, I left with a transformed heart. The Korean pilgrimage group became my family. We suffered together, laughed together, and grew together."</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic text-sm" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">"冒険のために来て、変容した心を持って去りました。韓国の巡礼団が私の家族になりました。共に苦しみ、共に笑い、共に成長しました。"</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic text-sm" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">"모험을 위해 왔지만, 변화된 마음을 가지고 떠났습니다. 한국 순례단이 제 가족이 되었습니다. 함께 고생하고, 함께 웃고, 함께 성장했습니다."</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-kailash-gold/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">朴</div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-medium text-sm">Park Min-ji</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Seoul, Korea · 2023</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Story 6 -->
          <div class="bg-kailash-light rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-md">
            <div class="relative aspect-[4/3] bg-gray-100">
              <img src="/images/story-6.jpg" alt="朝圣者在玛旁雍错" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.parentElement.querySelector('.fallback').style.display='flex';" />
              <div class="fallback absolute inset-0 bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400" style="display: none;">
                <span>图片加载失败</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <div class="text-kailash-gold mb-3">★★★★★</div>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic text-sm" data-lang-content="zh">"在玛旁雍错湖边，我看到了自己的倒影。那不是我的脸，而是我的灵魂。湖水如此清澈，仿佛能洗净千年的业障。"</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic text-sm" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">"By the shores of Lake Manasarovar, I saw my reflection. It wasn't my face, but my soul. The water was so clear, as if it could cleanse a thousand years of karma."</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic text-sm" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">"マナサロワール湖のほとりで、自分の反射を見ました。それは顔ではなく、魂でした。水はとても澄んでいて、千年の業を洗い流せるようでした。"</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 italic text-sm" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">"마나사로와르 호숫가에서 제 반영을 보았습니다. 그것은 제 얼굴이 아니라 영혼이었습니다. 물은 너무 맑아서 천 년의 업을 씻어낼 수 있을 것 같았습니다."</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-kailash-gold/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">王</div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-medium text-sm" data-lang-content="zh">王先生</p>
                  <p class="font-medium text-sm" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Mr. Wang</p>
                  <p class="font-medium text-sm" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">王さん</p>
                  <p class="font-medium text-sm" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">왕 씨</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">上海 · 2024年8月</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Photo Gallery -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-kailash-light">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-4" data-lang-content="zh">朝圣瞬间</h2>
          <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-4" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Sacred Moments</h2>
          <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-4" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">神聖な瞬間</h2>
          <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-4" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">신성한 순간</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600" data-lang-content="zh">镜头记录的信仰之旅</p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Faith journey captured through the lens</p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">レンズが捉えた信仰の旅</p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">렌즈가 담아낸 신앙의 여정</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <div class="relative aspect-[4/3] rounded-xl overflow-hidden group">
            <img src="/images/gallery-1.jpg" alt="经幡与神山" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
              <p class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 text-white font-medium" data-lang-content="zh">经幡与神山</p>
              <p class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 text-white font-medium" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Prayer Flags & Mountain</p>
              <p class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 text-white font-medium" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">経幡と神山</p>
              <p class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 text-white font-medium" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">기도 flags와 산</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative aspect-[4/3] rounded-xl overflow-hidden group md:row-span-2">
            <img src="/images/gallery-2.jpg" alt="朝圣者磕长头" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-110" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
              <p class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 text-white font-medium" data-lang-content="zh">朝圣者磕长头</p>
              <p class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 text-white font-medium" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Pilgrim Prostrating</p>
              <p class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 text-white font-medium" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">巡礼者の五体投地</p>
